survey.music_making: i played saxophone in school/concert band and took lessons from age 8-17. I still play every now and then just for my own enjoyment. i can play guitar TABs and some chords. I dabble with piano.
survey.medium: apple music, youtube, my own collection
survey.habit_change:
i used to listen to a band/artist's whole discography. now i jump around a lot more. a song from an artist here, a song from an artist there.

 i'm turned onto new artists frequently from hearing their song in a tv show or movie and then expanding from there.
